&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;the context words will represent banking!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Find out a bunch of places where banking occurs in text,and will collect the sort of nearby words that context words.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When talking about a word in our natural language,we sort of have two senses of word which are referred to as types and tokens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;word-vectors&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#word-vectors&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Word vectors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;build a vector for each word,chosen so that it is similar to vectors of words that appear in similar contexts.&lt;/p&gt;
